Usage: deleteShield [-help] [-routes_only {0 1}] [-selected  | -nets <string>]

-help              # Prints out the command usage
-nets <string>     # Specifies the nets to delete shield. (string, optional)
-routes_only {0 1} # Specifies to only delete shield wires and vias.
                   # (enum, optional)
-selected          # Specifies to delete shield of selected nets.
                   # (bool, optional)